    <item>
      <title>Geopolitics - A Chess Game</title>
      <link>https://www.ghaaspoos.com/posts/geopolitics-a-chess-game/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 08:00:00 -0500</pubDate>
      <guid>https://www.ghaaspoos.com/posts/geopolitics-a-chess-game/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;President Trump Announced America&amp;rsquo;s FIRST NEW OIL REFINERY In 50 Years!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Brownsville, Texas. $300 billion deal. Backed by India&amp;rsquo;s Reliance Industries — the same company that runs the largest oil refinery on the planet in Jamnagar, India.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That&amp;rsquo;s the headline everyone&amp;rsquo;s reading.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here&amp;rsquo;s what nobody&amp;rsquo;s talking about.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TWO deals are happening at the same time. And most people only see one.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;deal-1--brownsville&#34;&gt;Deal #1 — Brownsville&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This refinery is built specifically for American light shale oil from the Permian Basin.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
